1. Should have a LCD which shows the current mode of operation like a) Adhoc b) Connected 
and when everything is working fine, it shows the instantaneous power
2. Ethernet/ Zigbee should also be an option
3. Web UI should allow time to be set at the click of a button, rather tha having to do 
so manually
4. Different amperage plugs should be made available
5. Communication should not be so tighly bound as it is currently. 
6. Should be an option to store the data locally in a SD card
7. Should have provision to send data directly to IoT services like COSM, SensorAct
